Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.48,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Build a wealth and then leave it to the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:22.00,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Familia, familia, familia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.84,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Familia, familia, familia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.52,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Build a wealth and then leave it to the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:31.28,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Familia, familia, familia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.04,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that's been waited on by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:36.16,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Blood so cold that it froze in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:38.56,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Only runs when there's money to be made
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.96,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Time been invested, baby, I've paid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.40,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,With the nights that I stayed up late, wide awake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.32,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,To be real, it's not a thrill I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.68,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,More like a table with family and a meal we couldn't eat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.84,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Don't want no wagon till my sister has three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.56,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,A Richard Millie for the time I've spent chasing the G's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.16,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,I wear time on my wrist for the years I gave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.96,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Been stepping on the road I've paved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.96,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Dont't rush, I'm respecting the wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.76,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Learned patience from pressure, faith from the wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:08.48,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Can't cut, no shortcuts to make
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.92,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Zero fucks left to give, only millions to make
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.00,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Can't cut no shortcuts to make
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:16.32,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,When I'm gone what I leave feeds the bloodline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.64,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,I leave it to the familia, familia, familia
